    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "定義：",
      "pageIndex": 59,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        350.65,
        176.92,
        364.1
      ],
      "id": "block-41",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 7,
      "marker": "○",
      "text": "資料中某些欄位缺少值，可能因使用者未填寫、感測器故障、系統錯誤或傳輸中斷導致。",
      "pageIndex": 59,
      "bbox": [
        136.12,
        375.73,
        518.32,
        414.14
      ],
      "id": "block-42",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 7,
      "marker": "○",
      "text": "缺失值可分為完全隨機缺失（MCAR）（如偶爾出現有跳過填寫的資料）、隨機缺失（MAR） （如高收入者較不填寫）或非隨機缺失（MNAR） （如特定族群不回應）。",
      "pageIndex": 59,
      "bbox": [
        136.12,
        425.65,
        524.76,
        489.16
      ],
      "id": "block-43",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "示例：",
      "pageIndex": 59,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        500.67,
        176.92,
        514.12
      ],
      "id": "block-44",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 7,
      "marker": "○",
      "text": "線上購物平台的用戶問卷中「年齡」欄位缺失。",
      "pageIndex": 59,
      "bbox": [
        136.12,
        525.75,
        418.05,
        539.2
      ],
      "id": "block-45",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 7,
      "marker": "○",
      "text": "智慧工廠感測器因斷線導致溫度資料遺漏。",
      "pageIndex": 59,
      "bbox": [
        136.12,
        550.71,
        392.85,
        564.16
      ],
      "id": "block-46",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
