      "depth": 7,
      "marker": "○",
      "text": "邏輯錯誤可能導致模型失效或推論錯誤，例如在皮爾森相關檢定中納入不合理數據，影響相關係數的解釋。",
      "pageIndex": 61,
      "bbox": [
        136.12,
        625.74,
        518.23,
        664.15
      ],
      "id": "block-96",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "處理策略：",
      "pageIndex": 61,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        675.78,
        202.15,
        689.23
      ],
      "id": "block-97",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 7,
      "marker": "○",
      "text": "定義規則：設定邏輯檢查（如年齡範圍0-120、金額≥ 0）。",
      "pageIndex": 61,
      "bbox": [
        136.12,
        700.74,
        473.52,
        714.19
      ],
      "id": "block-98",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 7,
      "marker": "○",
      "text": "審查：結合領域專家訂定規則、進行偵測與修正。",
      "pageIndex": 61,
      "bbox": [
        136.12,
        725.7,
        430.65,
        739.15
      ],
      "id": "block-99",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "depth": 4,
      "title": "（2）資料品質指標",
      "anchor": "2資料品質指標",
      "pageIndex": 62,
      "bbox": [
        70.24,
        100.82,
        180.4,
        114.11
      ],
      "id": "block-100",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "heading",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "當面對大規模、多來源、異質性的資料時，僅依賴人工檢查資料品質已不敷使用，必須依賴具體且量化的指標，才能系統性地發現資料中的潛在缺陷與風險。",
      "pageIndex": 62,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        126.86,
        521.08,
        163.94
      ],
      "id": "block-101",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "以下幾項常用的資料品質評估指標，能協助資料科學團隊在資料清理與治理過程中快速定位問題、訂定優先順序並評估改善成效：",
      "pageIndex": 62,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        176.9,
        517.91,
        214.07
      ],
      "id": "block-102",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "缺失率（Missing Rate）：",
      "pageIndex": 62,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        225.7,
        258.79,
        239.15
      ],
      "id": "block-103",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "衡量各欄位中空值或缺漏資料的比例。高缺失率可能代表收集流程異常，或該欄位不適合分析使用。對於預測模型來說，缺失欄位過多會導致特徵無法使用或降低模型穩定性。",
      "pageIndex": 62,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        250.69,
        517.91,
        314.18
      ],
      "id": "block-104",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "唯一值比率（Uniqueness Rate）：",
      "pageIndex": 62,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        325.69,
        302.11,
        339.14
      ],
      "id": "block-105",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "評估資料中重複紀錄的情形。若主鍵（如用戶ID、交易編號）出現重複值，將嚴重破壞資料的正確性，影響後續整合與分析流程。",
      "pageIndex": 62,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        350.65,
        518.25,
        389.18
      ],
      "id": "block-106",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "一致性比率（Consistency Rate）：",
      "pageIndex": 62,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        400.69,
        305.11,
        414.14
      ],
      "id": "block-107",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "檢查欄位格式、單位、命名標準是否統一。例如同一資料欄中混合使用 「kg」與「公斤」、或日期格式不一等情形，將造成解析與分析困難，亦不利於資料共享與再利用。",
      "pageIndex": 62,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        425.65,
        519.55,
        489.16
      ],
      "id": "block-108",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "異常值比率（Outlier Rate）：",
      "pageIndex": 62,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        500.67,
        279.19,
        514.12
      ],
      "id": "block-109",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "計算明顯偏離正常分佈或上下限的數值比例，常透過Z-score、IQR 或模型式異常偵測法自動識別。異常值可能源自輸入錯誤、轉碼問題，或真實但罕見的行為，因此需搭配領域知識謹慎判讀。",
      "pageIndex": 62,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        525.75,
        518.4,
        589.12
      ],
      "id": "block-110",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "完整性比率（Completeness Rate）：",
      "pageIndex": 62,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        600.75,
        313.99,
        614.2
      ],
      "id": "block-111",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "評估觀察對象是否具備足夠資料描述。例如使用者資料中是否同時包含個人資料與行為記錄，若缺漏其中之一，將限制分析模型的應用。",
      "pageIndex": 62,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        625.74,
        517.85,
        664.15
      ],
      "id": "block-112",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "這些指標不僅用於靜態資料品質檢查，也能內嵌至資料流管線（Data Pipeline） 與資料品質監控系統中，建立自動化偵測與回報機制，確保長期資料品質穩定。",
      "pageIndex": 62,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        684.1,
        524.76,
        771.78
      ],
      "id": "block-113",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c4",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    }
  ],
